➜海南这些村庄入选全国乡村旅游重点村，你pick哪个？
http://www.sohu.com/a/417259935_376420	28110
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200909/b2ce73f6918541d1b44c283ac8946c1d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你是否憧憬过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远离喧嚣的城市</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">择一处山清水秀的乡村小院</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">追寻心中的田园情怀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">幻想着村边流水潺潺</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">村中绿树成荫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绘上精美壁画的民房</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">错落在绿荫间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与蜿蜒的崭新柏油路相映成趣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200909/ebac8ba6921a472596bff0c90519d41e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200909/5b955d82c9cd41af8cce7e43dbfc3934.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
